        "rendered": "\u00a0Edan Barukh"
    },
    "content": {
        "rendered": "\n<div class=\"wp-block-gutenverse-divider guten-element guten-divider guten-jBXkeU\"><div class=\"guten-divider-wrapper\"><div class=\"guten-divider-default guten-divider-line guten-divider-regular\"></div></div></div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"section-wrapper\" data-id=\"noxGUs\"><section class=\"wp-block-gutenverse-section guten-element guten-section guten-noxGUs layout-boxed align-stretch\"><div class=\"guten-container guten-column-gap-default\">\n<div class=\"wp-block-gutenverse-column guten-element guten-column guten-lBvXW9\"><div class=\"guten-column-wrapper\" data-id=\"lBvXW9\">\n<p>On October 22, 2023, the peaceful life of Edan Barukh, <em>20</em>, and his younger brother, Sahar, 25, was shattered when armed militants invaded their kibbutz. In a panic, Edan urged Sahar to escape through their bedroom window while he confronted their captors, determined to protect his brother.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>As Sahar fled into the night, Edan fought bravely but was captured. Days turned into weeks, and hope for Edan\u2019s return faded. Then, a chilling video surfaced from Hamas, showing Edan lifeless and bloodied, claiming he had been killed during a rescue operation.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Despite the heartbreaking news, the Barukh family refused to let despair consume them. They held vigils, sharing stories of Edan\u2019s kindness and resilience, transforming their grief into a celebration of his spirit. Edan became a symbol of strength and unity, inspiring others to stand against hatred and cherish the bonds of family and love in a world torn by conflict.On the morning of October 7th, Edan Barukh and his younger brother, Sahar, were spending time with their mother in their home in Bari when the piercing wail of sirens shattered the calm. Heart racing, Edan grabbed Sahar\u2019s hand, and they sprinted to the safe room.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>They managed to shut the door, but it jammed, and panic set in as they barricaded it with furniture. Suddenly, grenades exploded inside, and chaos erupted. Edan felt a sharp pain as debris flew, while Sahar rushed to his side. \u201cStay with me, Edan!\u201d he shouted, desperately trying to help.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>As the fire spread and smoke filled the air, Edan knew they had to escape. Sahar opened the door and stepped outside, but a gunshot rang out, and Edan screamed, \u201cSahar!\u201d</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Summoning all his strength, Edan leaped after his brother, but he saw Sahar frozen in shock at the doorway. \u201cGo!\u201d Edan yelled, but it was too late.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>In those harrowing moments, the bond between the brothers shone through. Though the flames consumed their refuge, their courage would never be extinguished. Edan and Sahar Barukh became symbols of bravery and love, their story inspiring all who heard it.</p>\n</div></div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-gutenverse-column guten-element guten-column guten-ovS2in\"><div class=\"guten-column-wrapper\" data-id=\"ovS2in\">\n<div class=\"section-wrapper\" data-id=\"m6hviM\"><section class=\"wp-block-gutenverse-section guten-element guten-section guten-m6hviM layout-fullwidth align-stretch\"><div class=\"guten-container guten-column-gap-default\">\n<div class=\"wp-block-gutenverse-column guten-element guten-column guten-B4tDYX\"><div class=\"guten-column-wrapper\" data-id=\"B4tDYX\">\n<div class=\"section-wrapper\" data-id=\"doTJt0\"><section class=\"wp-block-gutenverse-section guten-element guten-section guten-doTJt0 layout-boxed align-stretch\"><div class=\"guten-container guten-column-gap-default\">\n<div class=\"wp-block-gutenverse-column guten-element guten-column guten-M8VAQP\"><div class=\"guten-column-wrapper\" data-id=\"M8VAQP\">\n<div class=\"wp-block-gutenverse-image guten-element guten-image guten-b1VUJb\"><div class=\"guten-image-wrapper\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"gutenverse-image-box-filled\" src=\"https://iron-swords.co.il/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/candle.png\" height=\"3558\" width=\"1192\"/></div></div>\n</div></div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-gutenverse-column guten-element guten-column guten-ePb1WO\"><div class=\"guten-column-wrapper\" data-id=\"ePb1WO\">\n<h4 class=\"wp-block-gutenverse-heading guten-element guten-xRVPh8\">First Name</h4>\n\n\n\n<h5 class=\"wp-block-gutenverse-heading guten-element guten-1oB1By\">Edan</h5>\n\n\n\n<h4 class=\"wp-block-gutenverse-heading guten-element guten-PGSnJj\">Last Name</h4>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-gutenverse-heading guten-element guten-92jqc2\">Barukh</h2>\n\n\n\n<h4 class=\"wp-block-gutenverse-heading guten-element guten-ds3YVt\">Age</h4>\n\n\n\n<h5 class=\"wp-block-gutenverse-heading guten-element guten-nulT23\">20</h5>\n\n\n\n<h4 class=\"wp-block-gutenverse-heading guten-element guten-VaLm2x\">Fell On</h4>\n\n\n\n<h5 class=\"wp-block-gutenverse-heading guten-element guten-pCJMnv\">07 OCTOBER 2023</h5>\n\n\n\n<h4 class=\"wp-block-gutenverse-heading guten-element guten-x0HRME\">Army Unit</h4>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-gutenverse-heading guten-element guten-O4kY92\">Education Corps</h2>\n\n\n\n<h4 class=\"wp-block-gutenverse-heading guten-element guten-mdDvix\">Army Rank</h4>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-gutenverse-heading guten-element guten-gLnv9N\">Corporal</h2>\n</div></div>\n</div></section></div>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-gutenverse-heading guten-element guten-ElTnVu\">\u05d9\u05d4\u05d9 \u05d6\u05db\u05e8\u05d5 \u05d1\u05e8\u05d5\u05da</h2>\n</div></div>\n</div></section></div>\n\n\n</div></div>\n</div></section></div>\n\n\n\n<p></p>\n",
